This is the geolocation_blocks-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the geolocation_blocks blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'geolocation_blocks', which is imported as:

    import geolocation_blocks

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(geolocation_blocks)
